message: Made edits as discussed on talk page
Cleanup. Added sources. Removed primary source.
This page needs protection from repeated vandalism and disruptive edits. The users appear to have an biased agenda. Tabloids and private websites are not reliable sources.
/* WR Entertainment */ Moved litigation description of motions
General cleanup. Consolidated descriptions. Subdivided WR section. Added relevant details to timeline from articles.
/* Career */ uncredited reference with no relevance to the subject

Reduced the excessive use of sources which references the same think. Made a few corrections to language. Removed names of co-founders. Subject is clearly known as the founder, according to all sources.
/* WR Entertainment */Initial cleanup of WR Entertainment section. This page is subject to consistent disruptive editing. Requires cleanup of references, and semi-protection during process.
Removing defamatory editing that is based on non-credible sources.
Removed external site link. Not offcial
Removing protection templates from unprotected page
Made the article look slightly less like a job application.
Grammar (fixed run on sentences) and style (wrote it to be less like a cover letter and more like an encyclopedia article.)
